parts.text:
Slurm

{
"software": [
"Slurm",
"Singularity",
"Dask",
"Python"
],
"resources": [
"CPU",
"Memory",
"GPU (optional)",
"Network",
"Storage"
],
"configuration": [
"HPC_SLURM_ACCOUNT",
"HPC_SLURM_TIME",
"HPC_SLURM_NUM_NODES",
"HPC_SLURM_CPUS_PER_NODE",
"HPC_SLURM_MEM_PER_CPU",
"HPC_MASTER_WORKERS",
"HPC_MASTER_GPU"
],
"dependencies": [
"Singularity image",
"Dask library",
"Python environment"
],
"usage": [
"bash scripts/run_slurm.sh CONFIG SEED HPC_CONFIG [-d] [-r LOGDIR]"
],
"example": [
"bash scripts/run_slurm.sh config/foo.gin 42 config/hpc/foo.sh",
"bash scripts/run_slurm.sh config/foo.gin 42 config/hpc/foo.sh -d",
"bash scripts/run_slurm.sh config/foo.gin 42 config/hpc/foo.sh -r old_dir/"
]
}
